    "Unlike IMGAUD2VID, our idea captures more spatial information along with the holistic dynamic information of the scene from the image representations of audio.An optimal strategy to fuse features from different modalities is critical to take maximum advantage of each modality.",
    "Existing multimodal action recognition approaches have used fusion at early Feichtenhofer et al. [7], middle Roitberg et al.",
    "[48] and late Patel et al. [47] stages of neural networks.",
    "Different levels of fusion in the network have been tested by Long et al. [39].",
    "However, most of these approaches have used only visual modalities."
